00:05:48.730 --> 00:05:52.350
Mackonen produced and
presented a number of programs

00:05:52.350 --> 00:06:01.060
such as Shakespeare in Amharic,
Bridging the Gap, [inaudible] Jazz,

00:06:01.060 --> 00:06:06.070
biographical documentary, and
interviewed numerous Ethiopians

00:06:06.070 --> 00:06:09.490
and other African musicians
and artists.

00:06:09.490 --> 00:06:12.790
Mackonen made three
documentary films,

00:06:12.790 --> 00:06:16.660
including the Ethiopian
Thinking, a 22 minutes documentary

00:06:16.660 --> 00:06:21.230
on the brief history of
Ethiopian philosophy, in 2009.

00:06:21.230 --> 00:06:27.790
