Arts school in Ethiopia.

00:06:36.870 --> 00:06:38.890
And Heaven and Earth,
Church Education

00:06:38.890 --> 00:06:42.550
and Monastic Culture
in Ethiopia, in 2015.

00:06:42.550 --> 00:06:45.040
Mackonen at the moment
is doing research

00:06:45.040 --> 00:06:47.950
to make a two-hour documentary
on the political history

00:06:47.950 --> 00:06:51.600
of Ethiopia from 1900 onwards.

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:57.020
Mackonen is also a qualified
youth and community worker,

00:06:57.020 --> 00:07:00.780
