and hardship is also earth.

00:09:04.620 --> 00:09:07.510
So, I tried to just
make some comparison.

00:09:07.510 --> 00:09:16.530
Heaven and Earth, so all
together in that part of the land.

00:09:16.530 --> 00:09:20.070
