monks, and Ethiopianists,

00:10:00.730 --> 00:10:05.680
Ethiopian historians
and intellectuals.

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:11.630
And with all that I have
privileged to involve

00:10:11.630 --> 00:10:16.650
